==English==

Swearing was made popular in the late 1900's by Shanks of the Armitage.  Phrases included shitcunt, which proved to be a popular, but complex form of swearing, not to be attempted by amateurs or women.  Shanks went on to popularise several more inarticulate phrases but i can't fucking remember the cunts right now.

